                <div class="about-text">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded in 2015, Roman's Car Rentals began with a single vehicle and a passion for providing exceptional service to the people of Gaborone. What started as a small family business has grown into one of Botswana's most trusted car rental companies.</p>
                    <p>We take pride in offering well-maintained vehicles at competitive prices, with a personal touch you won't find at larger rental chains. Our team goes above and beyond to ensure every customer finds the perfect vehicle for their needs.</p>
                    <p>Today, we operate a diverse fleet of over 50 vehicles, serving both local residents and international visitors exploring the beauty of Botswana.</p>
